title: Grateful Dead Live at The Spectrum on 1989-10-19
lineage: DAT MASTER>Sony TCD-D10PROII>Sound Devices 744t>Soundforge 9(Fades/Sample Rate Conversion)>CDWAV>FLAC
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, West L.A. Fadeaway, Victim Or The Crime, Built To Last, Blow Away, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Cumberland Blues, Cassidy, Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> Dear Mr. Fantasy-> Hey Jude Reprise-> Death Don't Have No Mercy-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue

reviews.review_text: Of course No one knows how to write anymore. Let alone have a dialogue about the special time spent at these venues. So be it I'm still going to try. Immortal. Like Shakespeare. Think . Peace.
